The Spacious Master Bedroom has a large walk-in closet & is separated from the 3 additional rooms for privacy. The kitchen overlooks the large living area & features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & gorgeous ebony colored cabinets. This gorgeous home was just built in August 2019 and is ready for its new homeowner. Easy access to Hwy 287 & minutes away from tons of local shops & dining.  Being sold AS-IS
